item.title: Central Europe
item.author: taylor@teukka.tech (taylor thompson)
item.description: In Fall 2019, I took a trip around Central Europe. I visited Austria, Slovakia, Hungary, and Germany. Village in the German alps. Berchtesgaden, Germany. Budapest Skyline Wall in Budapest. Man at Work. Bratislava Church of St. Elisabeth. Bratislava. Hiking in the Budapest foothills Stag. Budapest. Vienna. Art History Museum, Vienna. Square in Székesfehérvár Aunt Kati statue in Székesfehérvár Stream in the German Alps. Fountain in Budapest. Székesfehérvár, Hungary. Clock in Székesfehérvár, Hungary.
